                <note rend="inline" type="source">881.512/30: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé at Tangier</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Rand</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-06-29T13:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 29, 1923—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>14. Your June 26, 3 p.m.</p>
                <p>Confer informally with your Dutch colleague and with the representatives of other
                    Governments whose nationals and protégés are not paying the consumption tax in
                    the sense of the last paragraph of the Department’s instruction number 260, May
                    8, 1923, and report by cable.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
